	<div itemprop="text"><p>But that&#8217;s my point. You don&#8217;t need to create a new post type to do any of what you&#8217;re talking about. What you want is just to create a new panel in the admin area with specific fields. You don&#8217;t need to create a post type to do that, you can do it with stuff that&#8217;s existed ever since WP 2.6 or thereabouts.</p>
<p>If all you want is a separate space to create posts, then create that space. Don&#8217;t try to create a whole new type just for it. It&#8217;s overkill.</p>
</div>

