		<div class="comment-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
	<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1307833951d8bc7f198a29d19866165e?s=48&amp;d=retro&amp;r=X' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />	<cite itemprop="name"><a itemprop='url' href='http://twitter.com/JAMikdiena' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Jānis no ikdiena.lv</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>	</div>

